                           </b></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                     <td width="15%" class="TableCellAlternate" valign="top"><b>Answer:</b></td>
                     <td width="1%" class="TableCellAlternate"><img src="/images/spacer.gif" border="0"></td>
                     <td width="84%" class="TableCellAlternate">
